8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Levity and Parabola share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. Where Levity pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Ai Actions, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Parabola uniquely offers Error Handling, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Levity holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Parabola scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Parabola comes in at a lower starting price of Free, while Levity begins at $49/mo. Parabola stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Levity requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
